  body " Sanskrit: {{tt+|sa|सेवि|n}}\n* Sardinian: {{t|sc|mela|f}}\n* Scots: {{tt|sco|aipple}}, {{tt|sco|aiple}}\n* Scottish Gaelic: {{tt|gd|ubhal|m}}\n* Serbo-Croatian:\n*: Cyrillic: {{tt|sh|ја̏бука|f}}\n*: "
  body "Latin: {{tt+|sh|jȁbuka|f}}\n* Seychellois Creole: {{tt|crs|ponm}}\n* Sherpa: {{tt|xsr|ཤའུ}}\n* Sicilian: {{tt+|scn|puma|f}}, {{tt+|scn|pumu|m}}\n* Sindhi: {{tt+|sd|صوف|alt=صُوفُ|m|tr=sūfu}}\n* Sinhale"
