  body "o|n}}\n* Sotho: {{tt+|st|apole}}\n* Spanish: {{tt+|es|manzana|f}}, {{tt+check|es|mela}}, {{tt+|es|poma}}\n* Sudovian: {{tt|xsv|vobale|f}}\n* Sundanese: {{tt|su|apel}}\n* Svan: {{tt|sva|უ̂ისგუ̂}}, {{tt"
