  body "h}}\n{{trans-bottom}}\n\n{{trans-top|countable: any variety of bread}}\n* Bengali: {{tt+|bn|রুটি}}\n* Chickasaw: {{tt|cic|paska}}\n* Chinese:\n*: Cantonese: {{tt|yue|麵包}}, {{tt|yue|包|tr=baau1}}\n*: Ma"
