  body "|သေလၵ်း}}, {{t+|shn|ၵူၺ်းၵႃႈ}}, {{t|shn|ၵွႆးၵႃႈ}}, {{t+|shn|ပွႆးၸိုင်}}, {{t|shn|ပွႆးလၵ်း}}\n* Slovak: {{t|sk|ale}}\n* Slovene: {{t+|sl|čepràv}}, {{t+|sl|tóda}}\n* Sorbian:\n*: Lower Sorbian: {{t|dsb|"
  body "ale}}\n*: Upper Sorbian: {{t+|hsb|ale}}\n* Sotho: {{t|st|empa}}\n* Spanish: {{t+|es|aunque}}, {{t+|es|pero}}, {{t+|es|mas}}, {{t+|es|empero}}\n* Swahili: {{t+|sw|lakini}}\n* Swedish: {{t+|sv|men}}, {{"
