  body "* Tamil: {{t+|ta|ஆனால்}}\n* Tashelhit: {{t|shi|macc|tr=mish}}\n* Thai: {{t+|th|แต่}}, {{t+|th|แต่ว่า}}\n* Tibetan: {{t|bo|ཡིན་ན་ཡང}}\n* Turkish: {{t+|tr|ama}}, {{t+|tr|ancak}}, {{t+|tr|fakat}}, {{t+|t"
