  body "t+|oc|fòra}}, {{t+|oc|franc}}, {{t+|oc|manca}}\n* Old English: {{t|ang|būtan}}\n* Persian:\n*: Iranian Persian: {{t|fa-ira|بِجُز}}, {{t|fa-ira|مَگَر}}\n* Polish: {{t+|pl|oprócz}}, {{t+|pl|z wyjątkiem}"
