  body "brew: {{tt+|he|מַשְׁקֶה|m|tr=mashké}}\n* Hindi: {{t+|hi|पेय}}\n* Hungarian: {{tt+|hu|ital}}\n* Hunsrik: {{tt|hrx|Gedrenk|n}}\n* Icelandic: {{tt+|is|drykkur|m}}\n* Ido: {{tt+|io|drinkajo}}\n* Igbo: {{t"
