  body "}}\n* Italian: {{tt+|it|bevanda|f}}, {{tt+|it|bibita|f}}, {{tt+|it|drink|m}} {{q|mainly apéritif drinks, both alcoholic and non-alcoholic, when served in bars or pubs}}\n* Japanese: {{tt+|ja|飲み物|tr=のみ"
