  body "\n* Ojibwe: {{tt|oj|minikwewin}}\n* Old Church Slavonic: {{tt|cu|пиво|n}}\n* Old English: {{tt|ang|drenc|m}}, {{tt|ang|wǣt|n}}\n* Oromo: {{tt|om|dhugaatii}}\n* Papiamentu: {{t|pap|bebida}}\n* Persian:"
