  url "https://en.wiktionary.org/w/api.php?action=parse&page=etc&prop=wikitext&formatversion=2&format=json&redirects=1"
  body "{""parse"":{""title"":""etc"",""pageid"":53120,""redirects"":[],""wikitext"":""{{also|ETC|etc.}}\n==Translingual==\n\n===Etymology===\n{{clip|mul|en:'''Etc'''hemin}}.\n\n===Symbol===\n{{mul-symbol}}\n\n# {{ISO 639"
  body "|3}}\n\n===See also===\n* {{langcat}}\n\n==English==\n\n===Pronunciation===\n* {{IPA|en|/ˌɛt ˈsɛt(ə)ɹə/}}\n* {{audio|en|En-us-etc.ogg|a=US}}\n\n===Adverb===\n{{head|en|adverb}}\n\n# {{alt form|en|etc."
  body "}}.\n#* {{quote-journal|en|author=Ramakant Sharma|title=Weld Testing Methods: Destructive & Non-Destructive|magazine=Cruxweld|url=https://www.cruxweld.com/blog/types-of-weld-tests/|date=2021-02-23|pas"
  body "sage=The aim of these tests is the examination of the weld without imparting any damage. These may include x-rays, hydrostatic tests, '''etc''', and are also termed NDE or nondestructive examination a"
  body "nd NDI or nondestructive inspection.|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20250525051126/https://www.cruxweld.com/blog/types-of-weld-tests/}}\n#* {{quote-journal|en|author=CaptBLI|title=Dawn Chorus "
  body "- Small game, Mississippi hunting laws.|magazine=w:Daily Kos|url=https://www.dailykos.com/blogs/Birds-and-Birdwatching?page=5|date=2024-10-20|passage=I visited several neighborhood parks that had exte"
  body "nsive feeder operations, trail systems '''etc''', and there were always family groups, often with very young kids as well as abuelas and abuelos, teenage boys and girls birding or hiking- it was reall"
  body "y eye-opening to see a people immersed in the natural world around them.}}\n\n===Anagrams===\n* {{anagrams|en|a=cet|ect.|'Tec|tce|ECT|CTE|CET|TEC|'tec|TCE}}""}}"

