  url "https://en.wiktionary.org/w/api.php?action=parse&page=greeting&prop=wikitext&formatversion=2&format=json&redirects=1"
  body "{""parse"":{""title"":""greeting"",""pageid"":69835,""redirects"":[],""wikitext"":""==English==\n\n===Etymology===\n{{surf|en|greet|-ing}}.\n\n===Pronunciation===\n* {{IPA|en|/ˈɡɹiːtɪŋ/}}\n* {{audio|en|LL-Q1860 (e"
  body "ng)-Vealhurl-greeting.wav|a=Southern England}}\n* {{rhymes|en|iːtɪŋ|s=2}}\n\n===Noun===\n{{en-noun|~}}\n\n# A [[conventional]] phrase used to start a [[letter]] or [[conversation]] or otherwise to ack"
  body "nowledge a person's [[arrival]] or [[presence]].\n#: {{ux|en|It's polite to begin a letter with a '''greeting''', but this practice is less common in email.}}\n#: {{ux|en|[[thank you|Thank you]] to ev"
  body "eryone who sent me birthday '''greeting'''s.}}\n#: {{ux|en|Send my '''greeting'''s to your family.}}\n# {{lb|en|uncountable}} The action of the verb ''to greet''.\n#* {{RQ:Churchill Celebrity|chapter="
  body "2|passage=I had occasion […] to make a somewhat long business trip to Chicago, and on my return […] I found Farrar awaiting me in the railway station. He smiled his wonted fraction by way of '''greeti"
  body "ng''', […], and finally leading me to his buggy, turned and drove out of town.}}\n\n====Derived terms====\n{{col|en|greeting card\n|greetingless\n|greetingly\n|greetings card\n|nongreeting\n|season's "
  body "greetings\n}}\n\n====Related terms====\n* {{l|en|greet}}\n\n====Translations====\n{{trans-top|acknowledgement of a persons presence or arrival}}\n* Albanian: {{t+|sq|përshëndetje|f}}\n* Arabic: {{t+|a"
