  body "ালাম}}\n* Bulgarian: {{t+|bg|по́здрав|m}}, {{t+|bg|приве́тствие|n}}\n* Burmese: {{t|my|ပဋိသန္ဒါရစကား}}\n* Catalan: {{t+|ca|salut|m}}, {{t+|ca|salutació|f}}\n* Chinese:\n*: Mandarin: {{t+|cmn|迎接|tr=yín"
  body "gjiē}}\n* Czech: {{t+|cs|pozdrav|m}}\n* Danish: {{t+|da|hilsen|c}}\n* Dutch: {{t+|nl|begroeting|f}}, {{t+|nl|groet|m}}\n* Egyptian: {{t-egy|njnj|h=n:y-n:y-A85}}\n* Esperanto: {{t+|eo|saluto}}\n* Eston"
  body "ian: {{t|et|tervitus}}\n* Faroese: {{t|fo|heilsa|f}}, {{t|fo|heilsan|f}}, {{t|fo|kvøða|f}}\n* Finnish: {{t+|fi|tervehdys}}\n* French: {{t+|fr|salutation|f}}, {{t+|fr|salut|m}}\n* Frisian:\n*: West Fri"
  body "sian: {{t|fy|begroeting|c}}\n* Georgian: {{t|ka|მისალმება}}\n* German: {{t+|de|Gruß|m}}, {{t+|de|Begrüßung|f}}\n* Greek: {{t+|el|χαιρετισμός|m}}\n*: Ancient Greek: {{t|grc|ἀσπασμός|m}}\n* Hindi: {{t+|"
  body "hi|अभिवादन|m}}\n* Hungarian: {{t+|hu|üdvözlet}}, {{t+|hu|köszöntés}}\n* Icelandic: {{t+|is|kveðja|f}}\n* Ido: {{t+|io|saluto}}\n* Italian: {{t+|it|saluto|m}}, {{t+|it|benvenuto|m}}\n* Japanese: {{t+|j"
  body "a|挨拶|tr=あいさつ, aisatsu}}\n* Kazakh: {{t|kk|сәлемдесу}}\n* Khmer: {{t|km|បច្ចុគ្គមន៍}}, {{t+|km|ស្វាគមន៍}}\n* Korean: {{t+|ko|인사(人事)}}\n* Kyrgyz: {{t+|ky|саламдашуу}}\n* Latin: {{t+|la|salūtātiō|f}}\n* "
  body "Latvian: {{t|lv|sveiciens|m}}\n* Lithuanian: {{t|lt|pasveikinimas|m}}\n* Luganda: {{t|lg|okubuuza}}, {{t|lg|okulamusa}}\n* Luxembourgish: {{t|lb|Begréissung|f}}\n* Macedonian: {{t|mk|поздрав|m}}, {{t|"
  body "mk|поздравување|n}}\n* Malay: {{t+|ms|ucapan}}\n* Māori: {{t|mi|waioha}}, {{t|mi|mānawa}}\n* Mongolian:\n*: Cyrillic: {{t+|mn|мэндчилгээ}}\n* Norwegian:\n*: Bokmål: {{t+|nb|hilsen|m}}\n*: Nynorsk: {{t"
